            p(style='text-align: center; font-size: 26px;') Service, maintain, and repair your residential emergency power!
            p(style='text-align: center; font-size: 26px;') We service over <b>1,500</b> residents in <br /> <a href="#map">the seven counties of the Hudson Valley!</a>
    hr
    div(style = 'width: 100vw; margin: 0; background-color: #ffa742;', id="commercial")
        div(style = 'display: flex; justify-content : center; align-items : center; padding: 20px;', class="flex-container")
            div(style = 'display: flex; align-items: center;', class="flex-item")
                img(src='/img/generators/industrialgenerator.jpg', style='margin-right: 10px;', width='250', height='auto')
            div(class="flex-item")
                p(style = 'text-align: center; font-size: 26px;') <b>Commercial and Industrial</b>
                br
                p(style = 'text-align: center; font-size: 26px;') Sales, managing and servicing more than <b>650</b> municipal commercial and industrial customers in <a href="#map">the seven counties of the Hudson Valley!</a>
    hr
    div(style = 'display: flex; justify-content : center; align-items : center;', id="maintenance", class="flex-container")
        div(style = 'display: flex; align-items: center;', class="flex-item")
