                br
                p(style = 'text-align: center; font-size: 26px;') Pricing Plans and Free Estimates!
                br
                p(style = 'text-align: center; font-size: 26px;') <b>For more information, contact us at: <a href="tel:845-344-1975">845-344-1975</a></b>